      "writtenOn": "2018-08-21T20:42:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is a bit tricky but I made it work.  The difficulty is when we have a Result\u003cvoid, Error\u003e, where we can\u0027t actually return an Optional\u003cvoid\u003e.  However, with enable_if I added a \"bool ok()\" overload for that.",
